defs.name: cpuid2
defs.value: fn (mut eax: u32, mut ecx: u32) -> CpuIdResult
defs.docs:
Execute CPUID instruction with eax and ecx register set.
 Note: This is a low-level function to query cpuid directly.
 If in doubt use `CpuId` instead.
